                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Each of these options can elevate your space while keeping costs manageable.</p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Enhance Lighting for a Luxurious Glow</h2>
